<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Polychora Records & Fulfillment</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Work+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style is:global>
      @font-face {
        font-family: "Poppins-Regular";
        src:
          url("/fonts/Poppins-Regular.woff") format("woff"),
          url("/fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf") format("truetype");
      }

      @font-face {
        font-family: "Poppins-SemiBold";
        src:
          url("/fonts/Poppins-SemiBold.woff") format("woff"),
          url("/fonts/Poppins-SemiBold.ttf") format("truetype");
      }

      @font-face {
        font-family: "Poppins-Bold";
        src:
          url("/fonts/Poppins-Bold.woff") format("woff"),
          url("/fonts/Poppins-Bold.ttf") format("truetype");
      }

      :root {
        --primary: #ffd753;
        --secondary: #f97133;
        /* --accent: #ffd753; */
        --accent: #ffdf9e;
        --tertiary: #ff5694;
        --background: #1a1a1a;
        --text: #ebebeb;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Poppins-Regular", sans-serif;
        background-color: var(--background);
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .container {
        width: 90%;
        margin: auto;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      header {
        background-color: var(--primary);
        padding: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      header h1 {
        font-family: "Poppins-Bold";
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--background);
        letter-spacing: 3px;
      }

      nav {
        font-family: "Poppins-SemiBold", sans-serif;
        background-color: var(--secondary);
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      nav ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      nav ul li {
        margin: 0 1rem;
      }

      nav ul li a {
        color: var(--background);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
      }

      nav ul li a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .hero {
        background-color: var(--tertiary);
        color: var(--background);
        padding: 2rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero h2 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .hero p {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 2rem 2rem 5rem 2rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        border: 7px solid var(--text);
        border-radius: 40px;
      }

      .section h2 {
        font-family: "Poppins-SemiBold", sans-serif;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .services {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .service {
        background-color: var(--secondary);
        color: var(--background);
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      }

      .service:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
      }

      .artists {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .artist {
        background-color: var(--primary);
        color: var(--background);
        padding: 1rem;
        width: 200px;
        text-align: center;
        transform: rotate(-3deg);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      }

      .artist:hover {
        transform: rotate(3deg);
      }

      .contact-form {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .contact-form input,
      .contact-form textarea {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        border: 3px solid var(--secondary);
        border-radius: 11px;
        background-color: var(--background);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: "Poppins-SemiBold", sans-serif;
      }

      .contact-form button {
        background-color: var(--accent);
        color: var(--background);
        border: none;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .contact-form button:hover {
        background-color: var(--primary);
      }

      footer {
        font-family: "Poppins-Regular", sans-serif;
        background-color: var(--primary);
        color: var(--background);
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        header h1 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .hero h2 {
          font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .hero p {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .section h2 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>polychora.</h1>
    </header>

    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#home">home</a></li>
        <li><a href="#about">about</a></li>
        <li><a href="#services">services</a></li>
        <li><a href="#artists">artists</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <section id="home" class="hero">
      <p>believing in unique artists.</p>
      <p>unfettered flows of creativity can be found here.</p>
    </section>

    <main class="container">
      <section id="about" class="section">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>
          Polychora Records is not just a label, it's a multidimensional
          experience. We're here to push boundaries, break rules, and ship vinyl
          to the far corners of the universe. Founded in 2025, we've been
          bending soundwaves and packing boxes with equal passion ever since.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="services" class="section">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <div class="services">
          <div class="service">
            <h3>Record Label</h3>
            <p>
              We don't just sign artists, we adopt them into our weird and
              wonderful family.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <h3>Fulfillment</h3>
            <p>
              We pack and ship with the precision of a drum machine and the care
              of a vinyl collector.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <h3>Distribution</h3>
            <p>
              We'll get your music to places you didn't even know existed.
              Alternate dimensions included.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="artists" class="section">
        <h2>Our Artists</h2>
        <div class="artists">
          <div class="artist">
            <h3>Quantum Quokkas</h3>
            <p>Psychedelic Surf Rock</p>
          </div>
          <div class="artist">
            <h3>Neon Narwhals</h3>
            <p>Synthwave</p>
          </div>
          <div class="artist">
            <h3>Fractal Flamingos</h3>
            <p>Math Rock</p>
          </div>
          <div class="artist">
            <h3>Holographic Hedgehogs</h3>
            <p>Glitch Hop</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact" class="section">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <form class="contact-form">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required />
          <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required />
          <textarea placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
          <button type="submit">Send It!</button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2025 Polychora LLC. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
